description:
Happy Memorial Day🇺🇸!
🇺🇸
While today we celebrate the memories of our forefathers for the freedoms which they have bestowed upon us, yet we must now also live with the restrictions that a global pandemic has bestowed upon us!
🇺🇸
Know that we are all struggling, whether it’s financially, personally, professionally or any other way, we are ALL IN THIS TOGETHER!
🇺🇸
So as we wait to resume our previously scheduled lives, be KIND, be COURTEOUS, AND MOST IMPORTANTLY BE POSITIVE + LOVING  because we are all sacrificing personally during these times!
🇺🇸
Have an amazing Memorial Day and have an even more amazing Summer Season!
🇺🇸
#JerseyStyle
#NoNewNormal
Love + Positivity = Success 
#LeRisqué
#GqQuarantineStyle
#LoveMoreHateLess
